dct_title_s: Jaffa Tel Aviv / Survey of Palestine.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Map shows municipal urban and village boundaries. "Surveyed 1932. Partly revised 1935." Map is a facsimile printed by the Survey of Israel, August 28, 2007.
